read the wish giver ! ! ! ! ! ! ! ! in school my class and i read the book the wish giver . this book is about three kids who each receive a magic card from a small , chubby , mysterious little man named thaddeus blinn . when each child makes a wish , the wish turns out the wrong way . the moral of the story is `` be careful what you wish for '' . this was a very interesting book . i really enjoyed it . bill brittain was a wonderful author . i highly reccomend this book .